OL,5,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FDealing with drug users and
OL,7,     Fdealers is a daily challenge for
OL,8,     Fcops. A driver, suspected of being
OL,9,     Funder the influence of drugs,
OL,10,     Ftries to evade capture, including
OL,11,     Framming a police car.
OL,12,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FDamo and the firearms team tackle
OL,14,     Fa supermarket gunman, while Gareth
OL,15,     Ffaces a death-defying pursuit
OL,16,     Falong roads and back alleys.
OL,17,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,18,     FBen Sutcliffe takes presenter Rick
OL,19,     FEdwards through interceptor
OL,20,     Ftraining. And Kev Salter goes on
OL,21,     Fdrugs busts, accompanied by rookie
OL,22,     FPete Tate on two of them.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
