OL,5,G1830 New: Home and Away
OL,6,     FSonny refuses to play by the
OL,7,     Frules. Cash's turnaround is
OL,8,     Fshort-lived. Justin catches a
OL,9,     Flucky break.
OL,10,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,11,     FThis week the staff at the Hall
OL,12,     FGreen Health Centre in Birmingham
OL,13,     Fare getting ready for another busy
OL,14,     Fweek.
OL,15,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,16,     FDocumentary series filmed inside
OL,17,     FBarnsley casualty department. A
OL,18,     Fbusy Monday becomes a
OL,19,     Frecord-breaker as the team deal
OL,20,     Fwith 349 patients.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
