OL,5,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FAt the Hall Green Health Centre,
OL,7,     FDr Ashraf speaks to a man who has
OL,8,     Freturned from a holiday in Egypt
OL,9,     Fand may have picked up something
OL,10,     Fwith serious repercussions.
OL,11,G0200 Casualty: Every Second Counts
OL,12,     FDocumentary series. Staffing
OL,13,     Fproblems hit the department as
OL,14,     Fseveral nurses call in sick. The
OL,15,     Fpressure takes its toll on Sister
OL,16,     FBenita, and she is herself
OL,17,     Fadmitted for treatment.
OL,18,G0245 Skin A&E
OL,19,     FInsight at a specialist clinic
OL,20,     Fwhere a team of top dermatologists
OL,21,     Ftreats a range of conditions.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
