OL,5,G0335 Friends
OL,6,     FThe gang head for Vegas to support
OL,7,     FJoey in his big movie break.
OL,8,     FHowever, the original plan
OL,9,     Fundergoes a few alterations.
OL,10,G0400 Teleshopping
OL,11,     FShop by phone from the comfort of
OL,12,     Fyour home.
